{"word":"κυματόω","slug":"κυματόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυματόω</b></el> <el>(κῡμᾰτόω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ώσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κῦμα'><el>κῦμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to cover with waves</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be raised</i> or <i>to rise in waves</i>, of the sea, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}